  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the feasibility of using indirect calorimetry (IC)
      within a comprehensive weight reduction program. Will individuals that receive a personalized
      nutrition program, at baseline, from IC technology respond better to treatment compared to
      individuals receiving IC technology at three months.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
